{
  "text": "In [CITATION_1] , we proposes a QoE-Based Scheduling Algorithm to control and adapt the packets transmission rate so as to reduce packet loss rate, jitter and delay, our study focuses on UGS service class. This paper takes into account the BE WiMAX service class using the Manhattan Mobility Model.",
